Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}胜负仅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}现在将其点燃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:48.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}焦躁不安  渴求着更多
